rows.label: tlk41100126_03_msg0001
rows.name: Ugh! Can't I win one single match?!

rows.label: tlk41100126_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Stupid Eluned! Why can't he at least
let me win once?

rows.label: tlk41100126_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I guess it's still fun, though, even if I
end up losing. I'm glad I've got friends
to play with!

rows.label: tlk41100126_03_msg0004
rows.name:
But that just sounds like I'm a quitter,
doesn't it? Just you wait, Eluned.
You're gonna get your comeuppance!
